{"tid":1323360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"受壓根本係藉口，咪放過部門首長，問佢責呀","createTime":"2019-07-16T08:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T08:49:07.000Z","uid":54442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d5576949baebd4c69e4b9634e2be97e5b78d9991","tid":1323360,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:16:38.000Z","msg":"咩警察執勤時受極大壓力，屌你老母，邊個打工仔返工唔係受緊老細極大壓力呀？？ 唔通我一受老闆氣就隨手拎起檯面個file車落老細度呀？<br />\n<br />\n做得公墓猿，人工包埋受氣㗎，頂唔順咪劈炮咪撚做，由你班警司老頂自己拆自己受囉。下屬爆鑊就梗係向上推莊啦，自己衝出嚟獻世咩，幫你老細孭鑊，上法庭做被告好，又或者出去送死又好，有乜著數先？咪撚俾署長同局長走撚咗去閃埋一邊，問責呀屌你老母！首長受罪，萬狗得救呀！<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再講受壓搏同情，心理唔舒服就去睇醫生請病假，公墓猿壓力支援電話熱線 2191 7299，狗房亦有專睇瘋犬症嘅專業人士坐鎮，瘋犬病患者咪再害人害物！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/admin/relations/471.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csb.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fadmin%2Frelations%2F471.html&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTedDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=36a6d714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/admin/relations/471.html</a>"},{"pid":"33b54c43b925e1625d2da150083694a0d906f847","tid":1323360,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有人冒警！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n推post時幫手廣傳有人冒警！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被動變主動</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"4afde95390a840a19a3bd2ec6ab8afec88a88725","tid":1323360,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1da0000ae6a5e38f42741ef8e5e1a326e2430e4","tid":1323360,"uid":181221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:27:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efee5ff334c51e8bdd56803e2a